data.description: Charming 2-story corner lot home, conveniently situated within minutes of uptown Charlotte, Camp North End, Northlake Mall area, I-85, and I-77. This property seamlessly blends its original characteristics with updated features. Enjoy spacious living areas, updated elements, and proximity to key urban hubs. Experience the perfect blend of comfort and elegance as the great room and dining room gracefully flow together, offering a spacious entertaining area accented with a fireplace and columns. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel and black appliances. The primary bedroom offers vaulted and tray ceilings with dual closets. Primary bathroom offers a garden soaking tub separate from the shower. Recently installed LVP flooring adds a fresh and stylish touch to the entryway, kitchen, laundry room, and upstairs bathrooms. The home was completely refreshed with interior paint of the walls and cabinets. It’s the perfect starter home!!
